text: haey chaur anak baoh dambng robsa anak choh . haey nowpel del keat bankheunh vea thveu chalnea dauchchea psa keat ka rt tralbtowvinh daoy min ngeak kraoy . ( pelnoh trong mean bantoul tha) ao mou sa. chaur anak kom phyokhlach aoy saoh pitabrakd nasa anakneasar min phyokhlach nowchampohmoukh yeung laey
